177
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,406
Tại sao?

178
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,411
Cậu là Neckbone, đúng ko?

179
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:26,521
Đúng vậy.

180
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,726
